Detailed Description

Generate different loading type of GestureRecognizer. 

 // Assume that we have a GestureRecognizer pointer named "mpRecognizer"
 // Here we want loading gestures from file by given address(stored in gaia::base::String path).
 mpReconizer = gaia::core::GestureLibraries::loadFromFileN(path);
